_comment: HyperFill Site Mappings — Is site/page pe extension uske hisaab se fill karega. Naye sites add karne ke liye 'sites' array mein entry banao.
_profileKeys: firstname, lastname, fullname, username, email, busEmail, email2, password, password2, phone, address, city, state, postcode, country, location, website, facebook, instagram, twitter, linkedin, youtube, title, company, category, subcategory, description
_urlPattern: Hostname. e.g. 'speakerdeck.com' → us domain ke saare pages.
_pathPattern: Optional. Same domain pe alag pages: urlPattern ek, pathPattern alag. Empty = pura site. Examples: '/signup' → sirf /signup; '/login' → sirf /login; '/account' → /account, /account/edit sab. Nested: '/account/settings' ko '/account' se pehle rakhna better.
_mappings: Profile key → CSS selector. e.g. 'email': '#email' ya "input[name='email']"
_category: Optional. Filter ke liye. Allowed: Article Submission, Web 2.0 Submission, Classifieds Submission, Image Submission, Video Submission, Social Bookmarking Submission, Document Sharing Submission, Local Listing Submission, Social Profile Submission.
_spamScore: Optional. 0-10, jitna kam utna better. Filter ke liye use karo.
_formSelector: Optional. Jab login+signup SAME URL pe hon: form ka CSS selector (e.g. #loginForm, .signup-form). Sirf us form ke andar fill. Do alag entries: ek formSelector #login, ek #signup.
_allMappingKeys: Total 27 fields. Sirf jo form me hai wo add karo; baaki chhod sakte ho. firstname, lastname, fullname, username, email, busEmail, email2, password, password2, phone, address, city, state, postcode, country, location, website, facebook, instagram, twitter, linkedin, youtube, title, company, category, subcategory, description
_generateMapping: Panel me 'Generate mapping from form HTML': form ka HTML paste karo, mapping auto banta hai. 300+ sites ke liye fast.
